<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/499001-is-it-necessary-to-know-a-lot-about">Is it necessary to know a lot about Hinduism or Buddhism in order to enjoy this book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_499001'><a id="like_count_community_question_499001" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/499001?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13821.Lord_of_Light">like</a></span>

