<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is a nonsensical question. This is a novel, not a role-playing game.<br/><br/>The character has the powers that he has. A more appropriate question is, doe<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is a nonsensical question. This is a novel, not a role-playing game.<br /><br />The character has the powers that he has. A more appropriate question is, does the story that's told about this character make sense for a character with such powers? It does.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
