          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781857988208" href="/book/show/756980.Lord_of_Light">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/60866073-baba?shelf=sfmasterworks">sfmasterworks</a>, 
